2. BUNDLED LANGUAGE DATA  (worddata/*.yaml)
================================================================================

The language-data files under the `worddata/` directory — specifically the
`lemmas:` and `verbs:` sections, and part of the `function_words:` entries —
are DERIVED FROM the Universal Dependencies treebanks
(https://universaldependencies.org/).

These data files are NOT covered by the Caveman software license in Section 1.
They are made available under the licenses of their respective Universal
Dependencies treebanks, which are predominantly Creative Commons
Attribution-ShareAlike (CC BY-SA) or Creative Commons Attribution (CC BY).

If you redistribute the data files (or derivatives of them), you must comply
with the applicable CC BY-SA / CC BY terms, including attribution and, where
ShareAlike applies, distribution of derivatives under the same terms.

See the accompanying NOTICE file for the Universal Dependencies attribution and
the list of source treebanks per language.
